java.applet.Applet
public class Panel
extends Container
implements Accessible

Unsafe: Panel is the simplest container class. A panel provides space in which an application can attach any other component, including other panels.

The default layout manager for a panel is the FlowLayout layout manager.

Since:
JDK1.0
